---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy policy" description="How Stay Safe Guide handles your data.">
  <article class="prose">
    <h1>Privacy policy</h1>
    <p><em>Last updated: 4 June 2026</em></p>

    <p>This policy explains what information Stay Safe Guide collects and how it is used.
    We aim to collect as little as possible.</p>

    <h2>Who we are</h2>
    <p>Stay Safe Guide is a UK-based website published by Iulian. You can reach us
    through our <a href="/contact/">contact page</a>.</p>

    <h2>What we collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Analytics.</strong> We use privacy-friendly website analytics to understand which guides are useful. This records general, non-identifying information such as pages viewed and rough country, not your name or precise location.</li>
      <li><strong>Cookies.</strong> Our own site uses few or no cookies. If we display ads or use affiliate links, those third parties may set their own cookies. Where required, we will ask for your consent first.</li>
      <li><strong>Email.</strong> If you email us, we keep your message and address only to reply to you.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Advertising and affiliate partners</h2>
    <p>We may show ads from advertising networks and use affiliate links. These partners
    may use cookies or similar technology to measure clicks and show relevant ads. You can
    control cookies through your browser settings, and through any consent banner we show.</p>

    <h2>Your rights</h2>
    <p>Under UK data protection law you can ask what data we hold about you, ask us to
    correct or delete it, and object to certain uses. To make a request, contact us.</p>

    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>We will update this page when our practices change, for example when we add a
    specific analytics or advertising provider, and we will update the date at the top.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
